│ 2088 /// recipe is placed in an entry block to a (non-replicate) region, it │
│ must have                                                                   │
│ 2089 /// exactly 2 incoming values, the first from the predecessor of the   │
│ region and                                                                  │
│ 2090 /// the second from the exiting block of the region.                   │
